OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBankers convicted of       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhelping Putin's friend     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Four bankers who allowed a friend of   
OL,6, Vladimir Putin to deposit huge sums in 
OL,7, Swiss banks have been found guilty of  
OL,8, lacking due diligence.                 
OL,10,FThe former executives at the Zurich    
OL,11,Fbranch of Russia's Gazprombank were    
OL,12,Fgiven hefty fines for helping musician 
OL,13,FSergei Roldugin, nicknamed "Putin's    
OL,14,Fwallet".                               
OL,16,FMr Roldugin reportedly paid in around  
OL,17,F$30m (#24m) between 2014 and 2016.     
OL,19,FHe gave no credible explanation of     
OL,20,Fwhere the money had come from.         
